1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Cantonese Subtitles
www.cantocaptions.com

2
00:00:06,612 --> 00:00:07,585
Mom

3
00:00:12,406 --> 00:00:13,299
Dad

4
00:00:18,139 --> 00:00:18,859
Bingo

5
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:24,654
Bluey

6
00:00:29,356 --> 00:00:31,047
-We're back!
-We're back!

7
00:00:31,913 --> 00:00:33,853
I'm so tired today

8
00:00:35,932 --> 00:00:37,732
Come chop some wood, kids

9
00:00:37,772 --> 00:00:38,619
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

10
00:00:38,953 --> 00:00:40,866
-Chop...
-Chop...

11
00:00:40,993 --> 00:00:43,219
Wooden

12
00:00:45,019 --> 00:00:47,867
It's time for bed in five minutes, kid.

13
00:00:47,915 --> 00:00:51,284
Let's wait another five years before going to this crazy world again.

14
00:00:51,324 --> 00:00:52,525
Let's play a game instead.

15
00:00:52,652 --> 00:00:55,192
You can play a game, but there are conditions.

16
00:00:55,248 --> 00:00:58,274
The game must be one where I don't have to move or speak.

17
00:00:58,314 --> 00:00:59,187
Okay.

18
00:00:59,574 --> 00:01:00,346
Bingo!

19
00:01:00,387 --> 00:01:02,726
Let's pretend Mom and Dad are mountains.

20
00:01:02,940 --> 00:01:05,085
Yay! Mom and Dad mountain!

21
00:01:05,966 --> 00:01:08,065
This time, Bluey's story is about

22
00:01:08,105 --> 00:01:09,483
"Mount Mumandad"

23
00:01:10,698 --> 00:01:12,296
Let's race to the mountaintop

24
00:01:12,491 --> 00:01:15,260
The first one to plant a flag on the summit wins

25
00:01:15,617 --> 00:01:17,332
Get ready

26
00:01:17,717 --> 00:01:18,377
Go!

27
00:01:18,417 --> 00:01:20,578
Wait, I need climbing gear

28
00:01:20,619 --> 00:01:23,176
It's tall, but we only have five minutes

29
00:01:23,297 --> 00:01:25,297
Don't start without me

30
00:01:38,084 --> 00:01:39,015
Got everything

31
00:01:39,056 --> 00:01:40,157
Get ready to start

32
00:01:40,250 --> 00:01:42,023
Wait, I forgot to bring the music box

33
00:01:42,063 --> 00:01:43,384
That's enough, Bingo

34
00:01:43,985 --> 00:01:45,997
I'm not waiting anymore, I'm starting

35
00:01:50,122 --> 00:01:51,542
I'm ready

36
00:01:51,589 --> 00:01:53,680
Hey, if you don't wait for me, I'll start

37
00:01:53,721 --> 00:01:55,661
How long do you expect me to wait for you?

38
00:01:55,709 --> 00:01:59,254
Then I have to go back and get some very important mountaineering equipment

39
00:02:05,522 --> 00:02:06,939
It's so hard to climb!

40
00:02:07,013 --> 00:02:08,959
Because your backpack has too many things

41
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:10,491
It's heavy, so it's hard to walk.

42
00:02:10,532 --> 00:02:12,912
It's all mountaineering gear.

43
00:02:12,953 --> 00:02:15,235
And Mom and Dad's hiking map.

44
00:02:18,419 --> 00:02:20,971
That's right, it means I'm not going the wrong way.

45
00:02:21,038 --> 00:02:22,299
Oh, it's Bingo.

46
00:02:25,472 --> 00:02:27,410
The scenery on the mountain is beautiful.

47
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:32,011
This mountain really stinks.

48
00:02:32,259 --> 00:02:34,199
I'm about to beat you, Bingo.

49
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:36,351
Let's take a picture...

50
00:02:36,391 --> 00:02:38,165
Bingo, what are you doing here?

51
00:02:38,206 --> 00:02:39,574
We are racing

52
00:02:39,615 --> 00:02:41,307
Taking photos… oh, that’s right

53
00:02:45,352 --> 00:02:47,432
It must be very difficult to get over there

54
00:02:51,913 --> 00:02:54,453
Help, I’m sliding down

55
00:02:54,519 --> 00:02:56,273
Help me, Bingo

56
00:02:56,345 --> 00:02:57,465
I’m coming

57
00:02:57,506 --> 00:02:58,850
Don’t worry, Bluey

58
00:02:58,890 --> 00:03:00,723
There’s a rope in my backpack

59
00:03:00,763 --> 00:03:02,216
Here, grab on

60
00:03:03,970 --> 00:03:05,304
Got you, Bluey

61
00:03:05,350 --> 00:03:06,697
Hold on!

62
00:03:12,235 --> 00:03:13,016
That was just luck

63
00:03:13,056 --> 00:03:13,963
Thank you, Bingo

64
00:03:14,004 --> 00:03:14,908
You're welcome

65
00:03:14,948 --> 00:03:16,656
But I'm still going to beat you

66
00:03:17,746 --> 00:03:18,955
Bluey

67
00:03:20,886 --> 00:03:23,271
Oh no, this slope is too steep

68
00:03:24,033 --> 00:03:25,300
And it's slippery too

69
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:26,112
Bingo

70
00:03:26,153 --> 00:03:28,867
Can I use your head to get some leverage?

71
00:03:28,907 --> 00:03:30,306
Hey!

72
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:32,920
Sorry!

73
00:03:33,780 --> 00:03:34,633
Bluey

74
00:03:34,946 --> 00:03:36,911
I'm about to beat you, Bingo

75
00:03:36,952 --> 00:03:38,471
How could you do that?

76
00:03:38,512 --> 00:03:39,653
That's cheating!

77
00:03:39,693 --> 00:03:40,892
I'm not cheating!

78
00:03:40,933 --> 00:03:42,752
Yes, you are cheating!

79
00:03:42,793 --> 00:03:44,692
No, I'm not cheating!

80
00:03:44,733 --> 00:03:46,652
Yes, you are cheating!

81
00:03:46,692 --> 00:03:49,565
No, I didn't cheat!

82
00:03:53,265 --> 00:03:54,207
It's ruined!

83
00:03:55,614 --> 00:03:57,221
Dad, stop!

84
00:03:57,711 --> 00:04:00,077
This time it's ruined, it's an avalanche!

85
00:04:09,186 --> 00:04:10,600
Bluey, are you okay?

86
00:04:10,659 --> 00:04:11,775
I'm fine

87
00:04:11,900 --> 00:04:13,311
It's just a small avalanche

88
00:04:13,351 --> 00:04:15,189
It won't stop me from getting to the summit

89
00:04:17,627 --> 00:04:19,630
Bluey, a storm is coming!

90
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:22,646
Dad

91
00:04:22,686 --> 00:04:24,020
Stop it quickly!

92
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,819
Bluey, hurry up and come down

93
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:27,358
It's very dangerous up here!

94
00:04:27,513 --> 00:04:29,865
I can't, I'm almost at the summit

95
00:04:33,526 --> 00:04:35,179
Bluey, come into the tent

96
00:04:35,219 --> 00:04:36,983
I can't, I must reach the summit

97
00:04:37,130 --> 00:04:39,010
You can't handle the storm

98
00:04:41,719 --> 00:04:42,836
Dad

99
00:04:46,703 --> 00:04:49,183
This ancient mountain is really terrible

100
00:04:49,823 --> 00:04:51,302
I quite like your tent

101
00:04:51,350 --> 00:04:52,096
Thank you

102
00:04:52,876 --> 00:04:54,025
It's for you

103
00:04:54,842 --> 00:04:56,216
That's great

104
00:04:56,323 --> 00:04:57,489
Thank you, Bingo

105
00:04:57,529 --> 00:05:00,549
We can play London Slapjack and wait for the storm to pass

106
00:05:00,590 --> 00:05:01,695
Good idea

107
00:05:02,176 --> 00:05:03,535
Black taxi

108
00:05:03,676 --> 00:05:04,741
Trafalgar

109
00:05:04,782 --> 00:05:06,542
Man in a furry hat

110
00:05:06,583 --> 00:05:09,015
Buckingham Palace

111
00:05:12,015 --> 00:05:12,731
-Slap!
-Slap!

112
00:05:14,961 --> 00:05:16,178
After that

113
00:05:16,385 --> 00:05:18,772
The rabbit ran very fast...

114
00:05:18,930 --> 00:05:22,529
So he left behind a very slow turtle

115
00:05:22,570 --> 00:05:23,850
Run faster, turtle

116
00:05:23,890 --> 00:05:25,348
Yeah, run faster

117
00:05:25,429 --> 00:05:27,754
Must beat that mean rabbit

118
00:05:32,490 --> 00:05:34,442
It seems the storm hasn't stopped yet

119
00:05:34,483 --> 00:05:35,836
So what should we do?

120
00:05:35,903 --> 00:05:37,739
Then let's stay in the tent

121
00:05:37,809 --> 00:05:40,489
We can watch the ballerinas spin.

122
00:05:47,679 --> 00:05:49,792
Bingo, I'm sorry for cheating.

123
00:05:49,833 --> 00:05:50,972
It's okay.

124
00:05:51,146 --> 00:05:53,905
Sometimes I'm the bad rabbit.

125
00:05:54,473 --> 00:05:56,979
Then I'm the slow turtle.

126
00:06:07,221 --> 00:06:09,961
Bingo, that big storm has stopped.

127
00:06:17,055 --> 00:06:18,969
The morning mountain is quiet now.

128
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:20,571
Here we go, let's walk.

129
00:06:20,612 --> 00:06:21,576
No problem.

130
00:06:24,748 --> 00:06:27,414
Don't wake this ancient mountain.

131
00:06:31,161 --> 00:06:34,099
If you want to successfully climb Mount Mumandad,

132
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:36,406
You cannot merely rush forward on your own

133
00:06:37,459 --> 00:06:39,946
Or leave your opponents behind to succeed

134
00:06:41,419 --> 00:06:44,280
But rather, you must slowly, carefully

135
00:06:44,646 --> 00:06:47,403
Rely on teamwork in order to succeed

136
00:06:57,283 --> 00:07:00,236
This is the way of mountain climbing

137
00:07:15,561 --> 00:07:17,561
Cantonese Subtitles
www.cantocaptions.com

